title: #92Noon! Paul Charchian/Wobby/Brian Robison
description: PA, Nordo, Paul Charchian, and Wobby start the week off at Vikings Training Camp once again, they're joined by Brian Robison to give their predictions of the upcoming season. Head coach Mike Zimmer gives his thoughts, and QB Kirk Cousins joins in the last segment.
